#### C.1 Regulatory Requirement Mappings

**Financial Services Regulations:**

| Regulation | Requirement | AWS Clean Rooms Implementation | Compliance Status |
|------------|-------------|--------------------------------|-------------------|
| **GDPR** | Data minimization | Automatic aggregation thresholds, differential privacy | ‚úÖ Compliant |
| **GDPR** | Right to erasure | Data lifecycle management, configurable retention | ‚úÖ Compliant |
| **GDPR** | Data protection by design | Built-in privacy controls, encryption by default | ‚úÖ Compliant |
| **CCPA** | Consumer data rights | Audit trails, data subject request handling | ‚úÖ Compliant |
| **SOX** | Financial reporting controls | Immutable audit logs, access controls | ‚úÖ Compliant |
| **PCI DSS** | Payment data protection | Tokenization, network isolation | ‚úÖ Compliant |
| **FFIEC** | IT risk management | Continuous monitoring, incident response | ‚úÖ Compliant |
| **GLBA** | Financial privacy | Customer data protection, access logging | ‚úÖ Compliant |

**Data Protection Requirements:**

| Control Domain | Requirement | Implementation | Validation Method |
|----------------|-------------|----------------|-------------------|
| **Encryption** | Data at rest encryption | AES-256-GCM, customer-managed keys | Annual penetration testing |
| **Access Control** | Role-based permissions | IAM integration, SAML federation | Quarterly access reviews |
