- **Technical Issues**: Maintain parallel legacy systems for 30 days post-production
- **Security Concerns**: Immediate rollback procedures with <4 hour RTO
- **Business Disruption**: Gradual migration with user acceptance checkpoints
- **Vendor Issues**: Alternative solution evaluation (pre-approved)

