## Appendix B: Cost Analysis

### B.1 AWS Clean Rooms Pricing Model - Accurate as of January 2025

#### Official AWS Pricing Structure

**Base Pricing Components:**

| Component | Price | Unit | Notes | Reference |
|-----------|--------|------|-------|-----------|
| **Collaboration Creation** | $0.00 | Per collaboration | No charge for setup | [AWS Pricing](https://aws.amazon.com/clean-rooms/pricing/)¬≤‚Å∞ |
| **Query Processing (CQ)** | $0.006 | Per CQ second | Billed per second, 60-second minimum | AWS Pricing Page |
| **Data Storage** | Varies by service | GB-month | S3: $0.023/GB, Athena: Query-based | [S3 Pricing](https://aws.amazon.com/s3/pricing/)¬≤¬π |
| **Cryptographic Computing** | $0.012 | Per CQ second | Additional for MPC operations | AWS Clean Rooms Docs |
| **ML Inference** | $0.015 | Per CQ second | For ML-powered queries | AWS ML Pricing |

**Compute Query (CQ) Unit Definition:**
- 1 CQ = 2 vCPUs + 16 GB RAM
- Minimum billing: 60 seconds
- Auto-scaling: 1-100 CQ units

### B.2 Total Cost of Ownership (TCO) - Revised Calculations

#### 3-Year TCO Analysis for Enterprise

**Year 1 - Pilot Phase:**
```
Monthly Breakdown:
- Query Processing: 10,000 queries √ó 30 sec avg √ó $0.006 = $1,800
- Cryptographic Compute: 2,000 queries √ó 45 sec √ó $0.012 = $1,080
- Data Storage (S3): 500 GB √ó $0.023 = $11.50
- Data Transfer: 100 GB egress √ó $0.09 = $9.00
- AWS Support (Business): 10% of monthly spend = $290
Monthly Total: $3,190.50
Annual Total Year 1: $38,286
```

**Year 2 - Production Rollout:**
```
Monthly Breakdown:
- Query Processing: 50,000 queries √ó 30 sec avg √ó $0.006 = $9,000
- Cryptographic Compute: 10,000 queries √ó 45 sec √ó $0.012 = $5,400
- ML Inference: 5,000 queries √ó 60 sec √ó $0.015 = $4,500
- Data Storage (S3): 2,000 GB √ó $0.023 = $46
- Data Transfer: 500 GB egress √ó $0.09 = $45
- AWS Support (Business): 10% of monthly spend = $1,899
Monthly Total: $20,890
Annual Total Year 2: $250,680
```

**Year 3 - Full Scale:**
```
Monthly Breakdown:
- Query Processing: 150,000 queries √ó 25 sec avg √ó $0.006 = $22,500
- Cryptographic Compute: 30,000 queries √ó 40 sec √ó $0.012 = $14,400
- ML Inference: 20,000 queries √ó 50 sec √ó $0.015 = $15,000
- Data Storage (S3): 5,000 GB √ó $0.023 = $115
- Data Transfer: 1,500 GB egress √ó $0.09 = $135
- AWS Support (Enterprise): 7% of monthly spend = $3,650
- Reserved Capacity Discount: -20% = -$11,160
Monthly Total: $44,640
Annual Total Year 3: $535,680
```

**Revised 3-Year TCO: $824,646**
(55% reduction from initial estimate due to accurate pricing)

